The paper is about face recognition using a neural network architecture, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the learning process of the network, which suggests that it may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image quality and resolution, which may suggest it falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of dynamic recalibration, which may suggest it falls under neural networks (cs.NE).
